data.title: PhD, Mathematics (Statistics & Operational Research)
data.meta_description: Profesor of Statistics at Escuela Andaluza de Salud Pblica. Expert Advisory for International Research Programmes. Coordinator of the Group DEMAP for Health Geography Research (www.demap.es). Director of Divestadistica, an on-line statistical divulgation journal (www.divestadistica.es). Country co-coordinator of the International Statistical Literacy Project 2012-2018 (http://iase-web.org/islp).
